race.comment: AUSTRALIAN LEGACY (8) is a filly by King's Legacy on debut for the Hayes yard. She's looked good off the track, winning a recent jumpout, and Stackhouse should give her every chance from the inside gate. FIRST FIFTEEN (9) resumes.  Ran sixth in latest jump-out at Cranbourne and she can be an improver with a spell under her belt.  ARWYN (1) came on strongly on debut to finish fifth and beaten 4 lengths at Sandown-Hillside. Can improve but prefer the place. ASK YOUR MOTHER (2) should be poised to run a big race first up from a spell following two recent trials - must be respected. BENRIACH (4) next best.
